HEADWORD: Notorhizal
<hw>No`to*rhi"zal</hw> <pr>(n⟦omac⟧`t⟦osl⟧*r⟦imac⟧"z⟦ait⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>nw^ton</grk> the back + <grk>"ri`za</grk> a
root.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having the radicle of the embryo
lying against the back of one of the cotyledons; incumbent.</def>⟦br⟧
